result.title: A few questions (solved)
result.content:
I was just wondering:

  1. What is the total number of problems in the problemset? Is there a way to see that number without having to count every time?

  2. What is the oldest submission? Can I see submission number 1?

  3. Can I see which users are online?

  4. Is there a Q & A section here? Could you give me the link?

If anybody knows the answers then please leave a comment!

Edit: Thanks to M.A.H.M.O.O.D and bkrtoni for answering!
